&lt;p&gt;   ReplicaManager should call ReplicaAlterLogDirsManager#addFetcherForPartitions even if there is already a future log since we can create an new ReplicaAlterLogDirsThread to handle the new partitions or update the partitions of existent ReplicaAlterLogDirsThread to make it busy again.&lt;/p&gt;

